      "rationale": "Experimental validation tests conducted at FDA CDRH facility under controlled conditions matching the simulation boundary conditions: inlet flow rates measured with calibrated ultrasonic flow meter (±1.5%), rotational speed controlled to ±10 RPM, blood analogue fluid (glycerol-water, viscosity matched to blood at 37°C ± 0.5°C). All test conditions documented in laboratory notebooks and traceable to NIST-calibrated instruments."
