      "rationale": "Quantitative comparison of CFD-predicted NIH against experimental measurements at 5 operating points. Mean absolute relative error = 8.3% (within 10% threshold). All predictions fall within combined experimental and model uncertainty bounds at 95% confidence. Validation metric computed per ASME V&V 20 methodology. Results archived in vr-hemolysis-bench-comparison."
