      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/morrison/criteria/validation-relevance-mrl2",
      "rationale": "Validation activities performed on the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump geometry, which is the same device class and operating regime as the COU. Operating conditions span the full 5-point flow-speed matrix used in the COU decision. Blood analogue fluid properties match physiological blood viscosity. Validation domain directly overlaps with the COU decision space, ensuring high relevance of validation evidence to the intended use."
